      "assistant_response": "Here's a concise summary based on our previous conversations:\n\n**Your Role:**\nYou are **Arjun Patel**, leading the platform team at **NovaRetail**.\n\n**Team Context:**\nThe platform team uses a production stack consisting of FastAPI, Postgres, Redis, and Qdrant. Service Alpha depends on Service Beta for inventory synchronization.\n\n**Current Reliability Priorities:**\nThe top priority is to improve API performance, specifically reducing the 95th percentile (p95) latency below **250 ms**. The current p95 latency is at **360 ms**. Additionally, ensuring high checkout success rates (SLO: 99.9%) and managing Redis cache TTL for product cards are important reliability goals.\n\nLet me know if this summary accurately reflects your priorities!",
