      "user_message": "Service eta will integrate with SendGrid for email delivery.",
      "assistant_response": "I've updated our conversation history with this new information.\n\nTo confirm:\n\n* **Service Eta**, responsible for handling email notifications, will integrate with **SendGrid** to handle **email delivery**, leveraging a dedicated service for reliable and scalable email sending.\n* I will keep this update in mind when discussing Service Eta's architecture, performance considerations, and any potential impact on downstream services or applications that rely on its notification capabilities.\n\nHere is the updated summary:\n\n* Release freeze extended to April 20\n* Service Delta uses WebSockets for real-time notifications\n* Team adopts Trunk-Based Development model\n* Mean Time to Recovery (MTTR) target is 30 minutes\n* Rate limiting implemented for all public APIs\n* Service Eta integrates with SendGrid for email delivery",
